Learn about Prcel bundler, documentation on parcel.org

Parcel, things it does

- Dev build
- Local server setup
- HMR hot module replacement, optimzied replacement to reload the site after any code change
- File watching algo - written in C++, to target only the files with modifications
- Caching - faster rebuilds
- Image optimization
- Minification
- Bundling - creation of single js files for all the code in the repo, in the dist folder
- Compress
- Consistent Hashing
- Code Splitting
- Differential bundling - to support older browsers
- Error handling
- HTTPs
- Tree shaking - remove unused code while bundling
- Different dev and prod bundles

read more at https://parceljs.org/docs/
